&lt;h4 data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Why Similarweb?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;Behind our global success and NYSE listing is a world-class Finance team spanning Israel and the US. We operate as a professional “one-stop shop,” where we combine deep knowledge sharing with warm, fun, and genuinely supportive work relationships. From day one, you’ll feel right at home. 🤝&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join a small, collaborative team &lt;/strong&gt;where you’ll have real ownership and the opportunity to make a visible impact. This role is a great next step for someone looking to grow their accounting career within a &lt;strong&gt;public SaaS company&lt;/strong&gt;, while helping shape processes and support a scaling business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Assistant Controller will be responsible for overseeing various accounting functions, including, but not limited to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Excellence&lt;/strong&gt; - Lead the month-end and quarter-end close processes, ensuring all journal entries and accruals are posted with precision in NetSuite.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance &amp;amp; Controls&lt;/strong&gt; - Maintain and evolve the internal control environment to ensure strict SOX compliance and adherence to corporate policies.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tax &amp;amp; Regulatory&lt;/strong&gt; - Work with external and internal teams in preparation and review of federal, state, and local tax filings, as well as registrations, and complex reporting requirements.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales &amp;amp; Use Tax Management&lt;/strong&gt; - Oversee the end-to-end sales tax compliance process, including monitoring economic nexus thresholds, filing sales tax returns, resolving state tax notices, handling complex sales tax inquiries, and overseeing the registration process.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Audit Readiness&lt;/strong&gt; - Lead the preparation for internal and external audits, ensuring proper documentation and compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Revenue Recognition -&lt;/strong&gt; Assist in the review of customer contracts and ensure revenue recognition in accordance with ASC 606.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Improvement - &lt;/strong&gt;Proactively identify inefficiencies in processes and implement automated solutions or workflow improvements.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🎯 This is the perfect job for someone who has:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3+&lt;/strong&gt; years of progressive experience in &lt;strong&gt;accounting&lt;/strong&gt; - Public accounting/Private industry mix is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;B.S. Degree in Accounting, Finance, or a related field - CPA a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High proficiency in Microsoft Office products required, with advanced skills in Excel (pivot tables, VLOOKUPs, IF statements) a must!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Problem-solving abilities that look beyond the surface, and are able to dig into the root cause of problems, looking for the “why” and researching the solution.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to research accounting standards and complex issues and apply them to real-world scenarios.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to prioritize workload and successfully meet strict internal and external deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;**At Similarweb, collaborating with our colleagues in-office creates a more connected, unified culture. Our best work is a product of our face-to-face collaboration, with the ability to work partially from home.**&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The base salary range for this position in the Burlington, Massachusetts area is $80,000 - $105,000, plus

