&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Business&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Development Representative &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;to nurture relationships with outbound prospects from enterprise and strategic accounts, turn them into qualified leads for our sales pipeline.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
