&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partnering with our marketing department to brainstorm and execute campaigns that show the value of our insights to our registered user base&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
