&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Data Analyst &lt;/strong&gt;to join the&lt;strong&gt; Data Collection Operations team &lt;/strong&gt;and contribute to the configuration writing, monitoring and big data analysis of Similarweb’s data collection services. This role involves working as part of a team responsible for ensuring the accuracy and reliability of our data collection processes across mobile and desktop devices.&lt;/p&gt;
