&lt;p&gt;As an account manager, you will own the relationship with these customers, and work with key decision-makers to make sure they are getting the most value out of our platform and data.&amp;nbsp; In addition to increasing your accounts’ user engagement and facilitating product adoption, you will be responsible for identifying and leading up-sell opportunities to drive new business growth.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;So, what will you be doing all day?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
