&lt;li&gt;Working closely with a customer to increase product adoption and engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifying opportunities for upsells, and increasing the lifetime value of our customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Making sure that our customers are getting the most value possible from the product, and reaching their business goals and KPIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
