&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;So, what will you be doing all day?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and execute regional marketing programs that drive brand awareness, lead generation, and pipeline creation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own regional events end-to-end, including planning, logistics, vendor management, onsite execution, lead capture, and ROI measurement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support GTM teams by organizing, and presenting campaign and event performance data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize regional marketing spend to maximize ROI across programs and activities.&lt;/li&gt;
